Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:08.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:11.39,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sent a little brat to collect my debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:12.46,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:17.50,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.50,0:00:19.29,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been winning today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:21.33,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's seven days' interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.33,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the money and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:26.33,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's get back to the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:27.21,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:32.71,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what you promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:36.84,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sugi asked you to pay your interest in person every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.09,0:00:41.85,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't just about paying your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:44.10,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take me for a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:49.86,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't press your luck, or I'll crack your head open and drink your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:52.71,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:54.07,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:55.86,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:01.04,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your jokes to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:03.08,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to say it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:04.86,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.86,0:01:07.05,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:11.53,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell me about your head-cracking skills {\i1}after{\r\fscx120} {\r}you apologize to Mr. Sugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:43.54,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... how may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:45.82,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle... do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:48.27,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you please tell me where to find Maeda Noboru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:51.93,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:55.52,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:56.66,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:57.65,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:02.75,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:06.91,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:11.63,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to take him to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:16.42,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you have your reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:26.71,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's currently out in Mishuku collecting a debt for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:27.68,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:32.17,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all goes well, he'll come back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:34.69,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The borrower isn't exactly the gentlest of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:41.35,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised I'd lend Noboru some money if he could collect this debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:42.45,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.70,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he need money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:47.95,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:52.96,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:58.96,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much does it take...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.46,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to grant your little dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.85,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noboru, you couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.50,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Mishuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:13.10,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.50,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:15.10,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.08,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against a violent—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.11,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:19.85,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing this for me—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.32,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:34.31,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, move your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.09,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.37,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.60,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.97,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really have to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:49.50,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, 'sup, Lily?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:51.07,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the long fa—{K.O}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.73,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:01.55,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:03.74,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:06.05,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:09.91,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:15.04,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:16.50,RAINBOW Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:32.94,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,"I had cried out of sorrow and humiliation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:36.41,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,but I had never cried out of happiness."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:41.29,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world barren of kindness and care,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:46.80,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle considered Lily as his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.85,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,For her sake, he'd put his life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:55.91,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily couldn't hold back her tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:00.31,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:04.67,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I finally get to see you in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:06.80,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.05,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:15.93,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He almost bit through my tendon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:22.72,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:23.49,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:27.45,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go pay my interest, so stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.11,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:35.69,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a scary-ass pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:38.67,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a "turtle" all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:44.00,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:46.92,RAINBOW Onscreen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(530,0)\fs56\b0\an5\pos(480,400)}The Next Day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:44.88,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.92,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm not going for a check-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.57,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break, Turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.41,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.84,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, Mario!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:53.43,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor said I had a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.35,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly fine anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.29,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Noboru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:57.31,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:59.85,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to get checked out properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:59.08,RAINBOW Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me— {added -juggen}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:03.31,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You survived the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:02.30,RAINBOW Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, Mario! {added -juggen}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:05.86,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:09.36,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told her, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.50,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:15.45,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you told Mr. Sugi that you needed money for your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.50,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You meant Lily, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:21.43,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:26.14,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think she was up to\N when you were doing that for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.71,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:34.80,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was taking some serious abuse to get you checked out at the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:39.55,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was... all you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.52,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:44.20,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:46.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily feels the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:51.31,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's worried sick about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:53.62,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're like a brother to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:59.33,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys are a family, you need to listen to your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:05.21,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.29,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Lily?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:11.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember ever having such a disobedient brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:18.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:30.40,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeffrey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.11,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to greet us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.32,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.97,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Maeda Noboru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:40.31,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be interpreting for you. I'm pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:42.03,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.91,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get going. {added -juggen}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.06,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Mario...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.87,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be away for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:49.42,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:51.56,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking care of a little business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:53.29,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out for Noboru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:56.43,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:34.13,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jeffrey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:38.43,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:45.06,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:47.13,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:51.06,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll get the results in a week, so I'll know then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:52.99,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.{added -juggen}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.20,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.07,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.09,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Jeffrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:04.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun boxing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:08.22,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Lily?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:10.30,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking care of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:18.50,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.70,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:38.61,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:43.62,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:50.76,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not lend Noboru... the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.32,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:02.84,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not lend Noboru... the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:05.85,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:09.35,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to disappear from his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:14.16,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, don't make him take any more risky jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.86,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.36,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:23.32,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:29.39,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how a family works?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.99,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}will{\i0\fscx120} {\r}lend him the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:41.43,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set him a test, and he passed it magnificently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:45.59,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a promise between him and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:47.14,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's because he—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:54.65,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it doesn't concern you at all, since you'll never see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:59.36,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.41,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.74,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:14.75,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you buy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:32.77,RAINBOW Onscreen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(530,0)\fs56\b0\an5\pos(480,400)}One Week Later
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.77,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The results from last week's check-up are in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:34.85,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:39.65,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing needing treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:47.41,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's still uncertain whether or not you'll develop symptoms from the bomb explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:52.92,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should get a periodic check-up, or so it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:57.85,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.29,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:04.91,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking so serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.85,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show a smile, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:11.06,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so carefree?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:13.06,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:19.63,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been gone for a week to "take care of a little business."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:26.57,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go there anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:28.84,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:30.24,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Mr. Sugi's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:33.58,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised you'd tell him the results, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:36.27,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.59,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.59,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here's your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:49.09,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:52.10,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't need this money anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:55.52,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is the tea ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:57.10,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.61,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:16.27,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the results were good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:17.88,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:20.65,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily, you're getting better at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:21.74,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:24.38,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:30.30,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on here, Mr. Sugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.34,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.65,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sex-crazed old bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:37.43,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bought her, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:38.77,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noboru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.27,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:45.78,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just to keep Lily from doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:49.64,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've tricked her with your stupid Buddha face!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:51.75,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:52.70,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.41,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:56.37,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario, don't tell me you're in on this too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.79,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:16.04,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:17.93,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:20.16,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:21.93,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:25.44,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You reacted exactly as I thought you would, so it was just too funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:28.46,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Noboru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:29.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:35.45,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the day of your check-up, I went to see Mr. Sugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:39.34,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you buy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:47.99,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you buy me, then I won't have to get Noboru involved, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:54.01,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:16:00.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He risked his life so that you wouldn't have to sell your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:06.62,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:13.61,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I told him everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:18.99,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I'd lived my life until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:25.00,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I was secretly stealing money from a U.S. Army general,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:28.48,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and how he swiped the cash back from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:33.76,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Telling him everything really made me hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:40.27,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should thank that general.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:41.32,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:45.53,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you had started a business with that money,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:50.78,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would've gone bankrupt in no time, because you don't know how to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.75,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:58.56,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Missy, the business world isn't very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:00.79,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you expect me to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:05.21,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:11.35,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This house...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:16.80,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little too spacious for an old man to live here all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:20.33,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you 15,000 yen a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:25.64,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can be the housekeeper here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.84,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll learn what it means to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:30.07,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and what it means to run a business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:32.18,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it takes a year or two,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:36.78,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll learn the principles with your body and mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:44.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maeda Noboru is still young, but he knows the mechanics of running a business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:47.86,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time you learn how business works,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:55.78,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll have transformed that 300,000 into something much larger, enough to open up a shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:01.08,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:03.73,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's why you live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:04.56,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.11,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:13.73,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry for saying all those horrible things!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:16.74,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave Lily in your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.02,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noboru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:22.62,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for lending me this money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:27.02,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, I'll work like a dog at One Percent Loan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:37.26,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:40.13,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you drank way too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:45.60,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that's because you passed the check-up and Lily's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:47.14,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be a load off your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.46,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:56.03,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why Mr. Sugi lives in that huge house by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:06.74,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I live in this big house all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:07.54,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.54,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:24.33,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they your...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:32.56,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wife left me, but I built this house for my sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:38.07,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have yet to receive their bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:44.71,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of their comrades saw them die,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:47.08,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm positive that they'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:52.22,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:58.54,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:00.72,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.55,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:04.79,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:10.13,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noboru's definitely okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:12.10,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:20.57,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it isn't, we won't let him kick the bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:22.96,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:24.81,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.58,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario, let's switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:31.75,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.12,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to carry him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.13,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:55.02,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,A load that's heavy to carry alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:57.60,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,is lighter when several people share the burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:03.07,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily understood the family bond for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:10.24,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,and she chose a way of life for herself and for Turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:16.06,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Noboru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:32.49,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A dream he can't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:36.66,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mario risks everything on one small chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:38.66,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:24.40,RAINBOW ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}sameta manazashi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:24.40,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}With my empty eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:30.74,RAINBOW ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}nani wo mitsuzukeru no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:30.74,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}what can I\Ncontinue to watch over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:36.32,RAINBOW ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}mamoru beki mono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:36.32,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}I can even sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:41.08,RAINBOW ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}kono mi sae oshiku wa nai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:41.08,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}my life for those\Nwhom I must protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:45.42,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Even if I rot away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:47.64,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Just keep on praying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:53.22,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}So far away, but\NI never give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:59.74,RAINBOW ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ima tokenai kizuna ga
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:59.74,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Our unbreakable bond {I= pretty liberal edit since it's more personalised}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:05.95,RAINBOW ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}unmei to kousaku shite yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:05.95,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}has begun to entwine with fate;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:12.50,RAINBOW ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}kagirinai mirai e tsuzuiteyuku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:12.50,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}guiding us to an endless\Nfuture that's laid out before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:21.44,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}And I will get over it, it's now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:26.10,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}{walk}a far-off distance.
